&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for an Associate Clinical Nurse Specialist band 6 within the Department of Diabetes at Alder Hey Children’s NHS Foundation Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a highly motivated, innovative and compassionate registered nurse, with expert clinical knowledge of diabetes care and a keen interest to work in this specialised area.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A strong interest in developing a proactive approach to the delivery of high standards of evidence based care is essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please apply if you are self-motivating, organised, computer literate and able to demonstrate excellent interpersonal skills, with a commitment to advancing diabetes care through collaborative working.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information please contact Kath Millar: kathryn.millar@alderhey.nhs.uk or Amanda Turton Amanda.Turton@alderhey.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
